data.description: This home is a stunning gem that has been well-maintained and offers ample room for everyone. You can cozy up by the fireplace in the spacious great room, have fun in the loft upstairs, or pamper yourself in the master bathroom. All new flooring throughout the house! The kitchen features elegant granite countertops and a custom wood slab breakfast bar, lovely cabinets, and a seamless connection to the dining and family rooms. There is a full bathroom adjacent to the downstairs bedroom. The main floor also has an office/den and a formal dining room that can be used as another living area. The property boasts a three-car garage and a hot tub. The patio has a charming pergola draped with tasty grapes when in season. And the community park is right across the street!
